author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Electrical box conduit tips…I’m using adapters for my conduit along with locknuts. Tightening locknuts can be a pain, but locknut wrenches make it easier. I like getting everything as tight as possible before adding the mud ring. By the way, I love the Makita low-profile organizer for electrical tools and supplies, it makes these projects a breeze 🔥#electrical #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #makitaadvantage #homerepairtutor
